title: Ep - 40 - Survivors Andrea Boehkle & Southern Charm's Danni Baird
description:
Andrea Boehkle explains what it is like to be a contestant on Survivor including whether you should gain or lose weight before going on the show, what happens if you get your period, and if you are allowed to use a toothbrush. Danni Baird from Southern Charm talks about her childhood, her brief romance with Shep, and what she thinks about Thomas and Kathryn’s relationship. Ryan Bailey helps Kate review this week’s episode of Real Housewives of New York.
